445
00:32:02,407 --> 00:32:05,274
<font color="yellow">(We are currently examining and fixing it.)</font>

446
00:32:15,477 --> 00:32:16,877
<font color="yellow">What's this, grandpa?</font>

447
00:32:17,087 --> 00:32:18,835
<font color="yellow">It's a car, of course.</font>

448
00:32:19,306 --> 00:32:24,282
<font color="yellow">It's my gift to you
for your first day of work.</font>

449
00:32:26,048 --> 00:32:28,796
<font color="yellow">- Grandfather, thank you!
- You're welcome.</font>

450
00:32:29,376 --> 00:32:35,565
<font color="yellow">He gave her a credit card to use freely
and even bought her a new car. She's lucky.</font>

451
00:32:39,399 --> 00:32:42,805
<font color="yellow">Drive carefully. Don't speed. Be safe.</font>

452
00:32:43,797 --> 00:32:44,939
<font color="yellow">Yes, grandfather.</font>

453
00:32:45,602 --> 00:32:49,877
<font color="yellow">- I'll drive you to work.
- Sure.</font>

454
00:32:49,902 --> 00:32:52,257
<font color="yellow">No! It's dangerous!</font>

455
00:32:52,282 --> 00:32:53,610
<font color="yellow">No, it's fine.</font>

456
00:32:54,235 --> 00:32:57,027
<font color="yellow">My granddaughter said
she'll give me a ride. I should accept.</font>

457
00:32:58,165 --> 00:32:59,365
<font color="yellow">Let's go, Shin-ae.</font>

458
00:32:59,595 --> 00:33:00,728
<font color="yellow">Yes, grandfather.</font>

459
00:33:01,274 --> 00:33:03,274
<font color="yellow">- Bye, mother.
- Bye.</font>

460
00:33:04,009 --> 00:33:05,368
<font color="yellow">Good-bye.</font>

461
00:33:15,063 --> 00:33:17,086
<font color="yellow">That fox has nine tails.</font>

462
00:33:19,931 --> 00:33:22,414
<font color="yellow">No. She's not a fox anymore.</font>

463
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:24,414
<font color="yellow">She's my treasure now.</font>

464
00:33:26,462 --> 00:33:31,595
<font color="yellow">Yes. I couldn't wish for more if
