468
00:33:52,281 --> 00:33:53,281
<font color="yellow">Yup!</font>

469
00:33:56,164 --> 00:33:57,517
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong, aren't you coming?</font>

470
00:33:57,924 --> 00:34:02,454
<font color="yellow">That elderly man is Winner Group's chairman?</font>

471
00:34:02,860 --> 00:34:03,860
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

472
00:34:03,885 --> 00:34:06,431
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong, you can't call him that. You need</font>

473
00:34:06,456 --> 00:34:09,058
<font color="yellow">to call him chairman. Chairman Kim. Let's go.</font>

474
00:34:11,392 --> 00:34:12,392
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong.</font>

475
00:34:25,243 --> 00:34:26,310
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

476
00:34:26,962 --> 00:34:30,610
<font color="yellow">I can't even believe
