478
00:34:37,079 --> 00:34:38,812
<font color="yellow">Ms. Kim! Ms. Kim! Ms. Kim!</font>

479
00:34:39,470 --> 00:34:41,800
<font color="yellow">We have a new director!</font>

480
00:34:42,079 --> 00:34:43,346
<font color="yellow">- Another one?
