533
00:39:55,995 --> 00:39:59,432
<font color="yellow">So don't wait for me, okay?</font>

534
00:40:02,448 --> 00:40:06,378
<font color="yellow">You didn't tell anyone about me, did you?</font>

535
00:40:07,331 --> 00:40:08,468
<font color="yellow">I didn't tell anyone.</font>

536
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:10,800
<font color="yellow">Good.</font>

537
00:40:11,425 --> 00:40:14,179
<font color="yellow">You can't tell anyone about me.</font>

538
00:40:14,753 --> 00:40:19,668
<font color="yellow">You can't tell the orphanage director
