539
00:40:23,066 --> 00:40:28,230
<font color="yellow">If they ask you who I am,
tell them I'm your aunt.</font>

540
00:40:29,214 --> 00:40:31,326
<font color="yellow">That way,
you'll be able to live with me later.</font>

541
00:40:32,269 --> 00:40:34,046
<font color="yellow">Do you know what I mean?</font>

542
00:40:38,300 --> 00:40:39,510
<font color="yellow">Okay, Yoo-jin.</font>

543
00:40:56,292 --> 00:40:57,292
<font color="yellow">Is it too dark?</font>

544
00:41:00,245 --> 00:41:02,393
<font color="yellow">No, no. This is good enough.</font>

545
00:41:04,963 --> 00:41:07,695
<font color="yellow">It's been a while since I wore a mini skirt.</font>

546
00:41:08,792 --> 00:41:11,307
<font color="yellow">What on earth am I
