547
00:41:15,347 --> 00:41:16,347
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

548
00:41:17,167 --> 00:41:18,432
<font color="yellow">Hi, Won-bin.</font>

549
00:41:18,909 --> 00:41:22,973
<font color="yellow">The wind is blowing outside,
