552
00:41:29,808 --> 00:41:32,432
<font color="yellow">Why? Is my outfit weird?</font>

553
00:41:32,956 --> 00:41:35,075
<font color="yellow">No, it's not weird at all.</font>

554
00:41:35,363 --> 00:41:36,830
<font color="yellow">It's totally my style!</font>

555
00:41:38,698 --> 00:41:41,643
<font color="yellow">Won-bin, go to the bakery downstairs
