560
00:41:57,105 --> 00:42:00,260
<font color="yellow">What? Can't I choose what I want to wear?</font>

561
00:42:00,464 --> 00:42:02,092
<font color="yellow">It doesn't suit my store.</font>

562
00:42:02,605 --> 00:42:05,401
<font color="yellow">I hate uncomfortable clothes like those.</font>

563
00:42:05,752 --> 00:42:09,520
<font color="yellow">Everyone else said I was pretty.
