00:42:13,349 --> 00:42:14,690
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

567
00:42:15,847 --> 00:42:18,314
<font color="yellow">Geum-sil has a good taste of fashion.</font>

568
00:42:19,370 --> 00:42:21,872
<font color="yellow">You should ask her for advice
