569
00:42:23,363 --> 00:42:25,515
<font color="yellow">What? Dress like her?</font>

570
00:42:25,711 --> 00:42:28,577
<font color="yellow">Yes! Sophisticated and ladylike like her!</font>

571
00:42:29,831 --> 00:42:30,831
<font color="yellow">Just like her!</font>

572
00:42:30,988 --> 00:42:32,565
<font color="yellow">Fine! I got it!</font>

573
00:42:32,854 --> 00:42:37,354
<font color="yellow">Take my sophisticated and ladylike
