580
00:43:30,917 --> 00:43:32,626
<font color="yellow">- Mr. Kim!
- Mr. Kim!</font>

581
00:43:32,652 --> 00:43:35,605
<font color="yellow">Call 119!</font>

582
00:43:35,630 --> 00:43:37,303
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim! Mr. Kim!</font>

583
00:43:37,328 --> 00:43:39,206
<font color="yellow">- Call 119!
- Mr. Kim! He's not breathing!</font>

584
00:43:39,231 --> 00:43:41,231
<font color="yellow">- Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!
- Mr. Kim!</font>

585
00:43:41,730 --> 00:43:43,417
<font color="yellow">Someone must have fainted!</font>

586
00:43:43,605 --> 00:43:47,354
<font color="yellow">- Call 119!
- Mr. Kim!</font>

587
00:43:47,379 --> 00:43:49,853
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim isn't breathing!
Hurry up and call 119!</font>

588
00:43:49,878 --> 00:43:52,612
<font color="yellow">- Mr. Kim, wake up!
- Mr. Kim!</font>

589
00:43:52,637 --> 00:43:53,854
<font color="yellow">Hold on!</font>

590
00:44:03,550 --> 00:44:04,760
<font color="yellow">Are they on their way?</font>

591
00:44:07,925 --> 00:44:09,782
<font color="yellow">Stop it! You'll make it worse!</font>

592
00:44:09,807 --> 00:44:11,074
<font color="yellow">Get out of the way!</font>

593
00:44:19,761 --> 00:44:23,307
<font color="yellow">It hasn't been long since
I came here, and yet,</font>

594
00:44:23,332 --> 00:44:26,877
<font color="yellow">I miss home so much. How did
